pos_examples: Now, calibrate camera dress_red on rover bastion using objective frame_9 at waypoint object_260.
Once you are done, please sample soil at waypoint yew using rover teddy and store in store star_213.
First, drop contents from store rain of rover bastion and then take image of objective roof_11 in mode fire using camera object_50 on rover bastion at waypoint yew.

(drop bastion rain)
(take_image bastion yew roof_11 object_50 fire)
The next step is to communicate image data from rover teddy at waypoint yew to lander kumquat at waypoint object_260 for objective roof_11 in mode screen.
(communicate_image_data teddy kumquat roof_11 screen yew object_260)
